Name: Highway Thru Hell
Title: Double Crossed
Desc: Mitch discovers a massive wreck involving two semis; Reliable and Aggressive Towing join forces.
LongDescription: Mitch discovers a massive wreck involving two semis; Reliable and Aggressive Towing join forces to recover a pair of entangled 18-wheelers; a tippy trailer abandoned on a soft shoulder tests Jamie; Gord finds himself in deep in a peat bog.
